OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbacks bid by MP Barry      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FGardiner to curb 'worst    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Labour is backing a bid to change the  
OL,6, law to curb firms' ability to lay staff
OL,7, off and take them back on different -  
OL,8, often worse - pay and terms.           
OL,10,FThe practice - known as                
OL,11,F"fire-and-rehire" - has caused several 
OL,12,Findustrial disputes.                   
OL,14,FA bill going before MPs on Friday says 
OL,15,Ffire-and-rehire should not be allowed  
OL,16,Funless employees are properly consulted
OL,17,Ffirst.                                 
OL,19,FBut the government has ordered Tory MPs
OL,20,Fto oppose the legislation.             
